{"word":"H7251 - רָבַע - râbaʻ - raw-bah' - Square - சதுரம்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>רָבַע"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râbaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-bah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Square / சதுரம்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நாலுமூலை, சதுரம், நாற்சதுரம்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to square, to be squared"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) square (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) square (participle)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (rather identical with <a href=\"#/H7250 - רָבַע - râbaʻ - raw-bah'/7250\">H7250</a> through the idea of <i>sprawling</i> at all fours (or possibly the reverse is the order of derivation); compare <a href=\"#/H702 - אַרְבַּע - ʼarbaʻ - ar-bah'/702\">H702</a>); properly to <i>be four</i> (sided); used only as denominative of <a href=\"#/H7253 - רֶבַע - rebaʻ - reh'-bah/7253\">H7253</a>; to <i>be quadrate: - </i>(four-) square (-d)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H702 - אַרְבַּע - ʼarbaʻ - ar-bah'/702\">H702</a>, <a href=\"#/H705 - אַרְבָּעִים - ʼarbâʻîym - ar-baw-eem'/705\">H705</a>, <a href=\"#/H706 - אַרְבַּעְתַּיִם - ʼarbaʻtayim - ar-bah-tah'-yim/706\">H706</a>, <a href=\"#/H7243 - רְבִיעִי - rᵉbîyʻîy - reb-ee-ee'/7243\">H7243</a>, <a href=\"#/H7251 - רָבַע - râbaʻ - raw-bah'/7251\">H7251</a>, <a href=\"#/H7253 - רֶבַע - rebaʻ - reh'-bah/7253\">H7253</a>, <a href=\"#/H7255 - רֹבַע - rôbaʻ - ro'-bah/7255\">H7255</a>, <a href=\"#/H7256 - רִבֵּעַ - ribbêaʻ - rib-bay'-ah/7256\">H7256</a>"}]}